name: Ogden_(smuggler)
content:
Ogden was a Human male who lived on Naboo during the Galactic Civil War. He worked as a smuggler and operated out of the city of Keren. Ruab was an associate of Ogden.
Ogden was a non-player character in the 2003 video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online roleplaying game developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011. Ogden was added to the game along with the smuggling missions introduced with the "Chapter 3" update, released on September 27, 2006.
